---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: The Monthly Retro
description: A high-signal monthly digest bridging long-form writing and curated discovery of ideas in engineering leadership.
permalink: /newsletter/index.html
---
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mb-4" style="font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;">
      The Monthly Retro
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      A high-signal monthly digest that bridges long-form writing and curated discovery.
      Each edition features a retrospective on the month's themes, the latest essay, and
      hand-picked reads with original commentary.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    {% set newsletters = collections.newsletter | sort(false, false, 'data.date') | reverse %}
    {% for issue in newsletters %}
    <article class="p-6 bg-bg-interactive-soft rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 ease-in-out border border-border-subtle">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">
            {{ issue.data.month }} {{ issue.data.year }}
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">
            <a href="{{ issue.url }}" class="hover:underline">
              {{ issue.data.title }}
            </a>
          </h2>
          {% if issue.data.subtitle %}
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            {{ issue.data.subtitle }}
          </p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="shrink-0">
          <a href="{{ issue.url }}"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-accent text-white rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-colors font-medium">
            Read Issue
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% else %}
    <p class="text-center text-text-secondary py-8">
      No newsletters published yet. Check back soon!
    </p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-bg-interactive-soft rounded-lg border border-border-subtle text-center">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Stay Updated</h3>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      Subscribe to the RSS feed to get notified when new issues are published.
    </p>
    <a href="/feed.xml"
       class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-bg-interactive-strong text-text-interactive-strong rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-colors"
       target="_blank"
       rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 5c7.18 0 13 5.82 13 13M6 11a7 7 0 017 7m-6 0a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0z" />
      </svg>
      RSS Feed
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
